FBIS4-39898 "drsov113_a_94009" FBIS-SOV-94-113 Daily Report 10 Jun 1994 RUSSIA INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS Russia, U.S. Agree on Sanctions Against DPRK Russia, U.S. Agree on Sanctions Against DPRK LD1006172994 Moscow ITAR-TASS in English 1608 GMT 10 Jun 94 LD1006172994 Moscow ITAR-TASS English BFN [Text] Istanbul June 10 TASS -- Russia and the United States agreed to submit to the U.N. Security Council's consideration the joint resolution on sanctions against North Korea linked with the nuclear programme of this country and hold an international conference on security and nuclear-free status of the Korean penisular, Russian Foreign Minister Andrey Kozyrev and U.S. Secretary of State Warren Christopher told a joint press conference in Istanbul on Friday. The resolution will be submitted to the U.N. Security Council's consideration "within the next few days", Warren Christopher pointed out.
